1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: Rick Edwards hosts the first edition of the brand new daytime quiz show in which 30 contestants face elimination from today's show if they choose an answer that is not just wrong but impossible.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: 30 contestants take part in the daytime quiz hosted by Rick Edwards. They will have to choose the correct answer while avoiding the impossible answer which will eliminate them from the game.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: 30 contestants compete for the chance to win ten thousand pounds in the quiz show where every question has a right, wrong and impossible answer. Hosted by Rick Edwards.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Rick Edwards hosts another edition of the new daytime quiz show in which the thirty regular contestants must choose the correct answer while avoiding selecting the impossible answer that will see them eliminated.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: The thirty contestants return for another crack at winning the ten thousand pound coins contained within the giant exclamation mark - to do so they will have to avoid choosing the impossible answer to each question.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Rick Edwards hosts another edition of the daytime quiz show in which thirty contestants try to avoid giving the impossible answer to questions to progress and try to win ten thousand pound coins.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Quiz show in which 30 players compete across the series, scoring points by answering questions correctly. They must avoid the impossible answers though, otherwise they will be eliminated from the show until the next day.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: 30 players compete in the quiz, scoring points for correct answers but are eliminated if they give the impossible answer. In each episode there are three rounds, the highest scorer from each round plays against each other in the final.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Rick Edwards hosts the quiz in which 30 players aim to score points by answering questions correctly while avoiding the impossible answers that will lead to elimination from the show until the next day.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Rick Edwards hosts another edition of the daytime quiz show in which thirty contestants compete for a chance to win a prize consisting of ten thousand pound coins.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Will one of the thirty contestants win the 10,000 pound coins contained within the giant exclamation mark? To do so they will have to answer the questions correctly while avoiding the impossible answers.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Rick Edwards hosts another edition of the daytime quiz in which thirty contestants hope to avoid the impossible answers on the way to attempting to win ten thousand pounds.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Rick Edwards host another edition of the daytime quiz show in which thirty contestants try to avoid the impossible answers to have the chance to win a cash prize of ten thousand pounds.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Rick Edwards hosts the penultimate edition of the quiz show in which a panel of thirty recurring contestants try to avoid the impossible answers to be in with a chance of winning 10,000 pounds.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: The thirty contestants have one final chance to reach the final and get the chance to win the 10,000 pound coins sitting in the giant exclamation mark in the daytime quiz hosted by Rick Edwards.
